sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Settings UI
    participant REST as REST PUT /api/settings/physics
    participant OSA as OptimizedSettingsActor
    participant Neo4j as Neo4j Persistence
    participant FCA as ForceComputeActor (GPU)
    participant GSS as GraphServiceSupervisor
    participant POA as PhysicsOrchestratorActor
    participant GSA as GraphStateActor
    participant CCA as ClientCoordinatorActor

    UI->>REST: PUT physics JSON patch
    REST->>OSA: GetSettings
    OSA-->>REST: AppFullSettings snapshot
    REST->>REST: Merge patch, validate, normalize keys
    REST->>OSA: UpdateSettings{merged}
    OSA-->>REST: Ok

    Note over REST: Propagate to GPU actors

    REST->>FCA: UpdateSimulationParams (direct via AppState)
    FCA->>FCA: Idempotency check (skip if unchanged)
    FCA->>FCA: Update sim_params + unified_params
    FCA->>FCA: Reset stability_warmup_remaining
    FCA->>FCA: Reset broadcast_optimizer delta state

    REST->>GSS: UpdateSimulationParams
    GSS->>POA: Forward UpdateSimulationParams
    POA->>POA: Detect physics_changed
    POA->>POA: Reset fast_settle state
    POA->>POA: Reset equilibrium_stability_counter = 0
    POA->>POA: Set is_physics_paused = false
    POA->>POA: broadcast_physics_resumed()
    POA->>FCA: do_send(UpdateSimulationParams) (guaranteed fallback)

    rect rgb(200, 255, 200)
        Note over REST: FIX: Send ForceResumePhysics
        REST->>GSS: ForceResumePhysics{reason: "settings changed"}
        GSS->>POA: Forward ForceResumePhysics
        POA->>POA: resume_physics() -- force simulation_running = true
        POA->>POA: schedule_next_pipeline_step(ZERO)
    end

    Note over POA: Sequential pipeline restarts
    POA->>FCA: ComputeForces
    FCA->>FCA: GPU kernel execution (CUDA)
    FCA->>FCA: Read positions from GPU
    FCA-->>POA: PhysicsStepCompleted{KE, iteration}
    POA->>POA: check_equilibrium (KE vs threshold)

    rect rgb(200, 255, 200)
        Note over POA,CCA: FIX: Broadcast updated positions
        POA->>GSS: UpdateNodePositions
        GSS->>CCA: BroadcastPositions
        CCA->>UI: WebSocket binary position data
    end

    REST-->>Neo4j: Persist physics JSON (async)
